<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="confirm-vt">confirm <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'fɜːm/    美 /kən'fɜːrm/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>证实；证明：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The experiment confirmed his theory.
这个实验证实了他的理论。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>confirm + (that) / wh- 从句：</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Research has confirmed that the risk is higher for women.
研究已经证实，这种风险在女性中的比例更高。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>确认 (安排、日期或情况)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>confirm a booking / reservation</strong>
确认预订</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Six people have <strong>confirmed that</strong> they will be attending the conference. 
已经有6人确定要参加这次会议。</p></div></div>